## Project Overview
We are building a Pakistani university admission portal powered by Google ADK (Agent Development Kit).
Each student gets their own personal portal (unique USER_ID + SESSION_ID) to track admissions across top Pakistani universities.
The agent answers queries, calculates merit, checks deadlines, compares universities, and fetches live info via Google Search.

## Tech Stack
- Language: Python
- Framework: Google ADK (google-adk)
- Memory: ADK Persistent Memory
- Search: Google Search Tool (built into ADK)
- Architecture: Multi-agent (agent team)

