## Universities in Scope (v1)
Only these 5 universities are in scope for v1:

| University | Entry Test | Test Total |
|------------|------------|------------|
| NUST       | NET        | 200        |
| FAST       | NU Test / NAT | 100     |
| UET Lahore | ECAT       | 400        |
| COMSATS    | NTS-NAT    | 100        |
| Air University | AU-CBT | 100        |

IBA and Aga Khan University are excluded from v1 (their merit systems are non-formula based).

