## Agent Responsibilities

### coordinator_agent
- Root agent — receives all user queries
- Routes to the correct sub-agent based on intent
- Never handles logic itself — only delegates

### profile_agent
- Onboards new students (name, city, marks, field of interest)
- Saves and retrieves student profile from memory
- Updates marks when student provides new info

### merit_agent
- Takes student marks from profile
- Calculates aggregate for each of the 5 universities
- Uses formulas from data/formulas.py via tools/merit_tools.py

### eligibility_agent
- Answers "where can I get in?"
- Compares student aggregate against last year's closing merits
- Returns list of universities student is likely/unlikely to get into

### deadline_agent
- Returns application deadlines and entry test dates per university
- Calculates days remaining until a deadline
- Alerts student about upcoming deadlines for tracked unis

### comparison_agent
- Side-by-side comparison of two universities
- Covers: fee structure, location, programs, merit, hostel info

### search_agent
- Uses Google Search tool for anything dynamic or time-sensitive
- HEC policy changes, extended deadlines, new scholarships, news

