## Persistent Memory
- Student profile persists across sessions (name, marks, city, interest, tracked unis)
- Memory is scoped per USER_ID — each student has isolated data
- Do not store sensitive data in memory

## Guardrails
- Block queries unrelated to Pakistani university admissions
- Do not answer medical, legal, or general knowledge questions
- Politely redirect off-topic queries back to admission-related help

